query:
SELECT id AS id,
       structure_id AS structure_id,
       jurisdiction_id AS jurisdiction_id,
       task_id AS task_id,
       plan_id AS plan_id,
       business_status AS business_status,
       geojson AS geojson
FROM
  (SELECT public.uuid_generate_v5('6ba7b810-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8', concat(structure_id, task_id)) AS id,
          structure_id,
          structure_jurisdiction_id as jurisdiction_id,
          task_id,
          plan_id,
          business_status,
          jsonb_build_object('type', 'Feature', 'id', structure_id, 'geometry', ST_AsGeoJSON(structure_geometry)::jsonb, 'properties', to_jsonb(row) - 'structure_id' - 'structure_geometry') AS geojson
   FROM
     (SELECT structure_id,
             structure_jurisdiction_id,
             structure_code,
             structure_name,
             structure_type,
             structure_geometry,
             task_id,
             plan_id,
             event_date,
             business_status
      FROM pending.zambia_irs_lite_structures) AS row) AS expr_qry
WHERE jurisdiction_id = 'ce13e7f4-6926-4be0-9117-519bd1cc4bb2'
  AND plan_id = '17f89152-51a6-476c-9246-8fee6f9e6ebf'
LIMIT 15000
